'One very important setting here is the \'always notify\' field for each member of the team. If this is set to true then that person will receive all the notifications that come to the team from the event manager. If you want you can have all the members of the team receive these notifications. But at least you would want the team leader to have this set to true.' => '这里一个非常重要的设置是团队中每个成员的“始终通知”字段。如果将此设置为true，则该人员将从事件管理器接收来自团队的所有通知。如果您愿意，您可以让团队的所有成员都收到这些通知。但至少你会希望团队领导者将此设置为真。',
'Only fill in this if \'Use an automatically created subject\' is false (not checked). This will then be the subject of the email.' => '如果“使用自动创建的主题”为false（未选中），则仅填写此内容。这将是电子邮件的主题。',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Accept Button\' is true. In that case you must enter some positive text.' => '如果“显示接受按钮”为真，则仅填写此内容。在这种情况下，您必须输入一些正文。',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Link To Object\' is true. Write something that shows that this is a link to the event' => '如果“Show Link To Object”为true，则仅填写此内容。写一些东西，表明这是一个事件的链接',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Reject Button\' is true. In that case you must enter some text showing a negative response.' => '如果“显示拒绝按钮”为真，则仅填写此内容。在这种情况下，您必须输入一些显示否定回复的文本。',
