'Show Reject Button' => '显示拒绝按钮',
'Simply put a name here describing what the message is about. For example: Demand response, Empty email, Reminder' => '只需在此处输入一个名称来描述消息的内容。例如：需求响应，空电子邮件，提醒',
'Smartphone' => '手机',
'Song' => '歌曲',
'Song attachement' => '宋附庸',
'Song database with CSV and OpenLP import and CSV export.' => '具有CSV和OpenLP导入和CSV导出的Song数据库。',
'Songs are a central part of many worship services. Here also they have a central role. There are usually so many songs that it is unreasonable to type in them all by hand. That is why you have the CSV import and the OpenLP import.' => '歌曲是许多崇拜服务的核心部分。他们在这里也发挥着核心作用。通常有这么多的歌曲，手动输入它们是不合理的。这就是您进行CSV导入和OpenLP导入的原因。',
'Special needs' => '特殊需求',
'Status' => '状态',
'Subject' => '学科',
'Table of contents' => '目录',
'Task templates' => '任务模板',
'Tasks' => '任务',
'Tasks are easy to define with a multitude of possibilities' => '任务很容易定义，具有多种可能性',
'Tasks may also be accepted or rejected by the user inside of the program instead of by email.' => '用户也可以在程序内部而不是通过电子邮件接受或拒绝任务。',
'Team' => '球队',
'Team Manager' => '团队经理',
'Team Type' => '团队类型',
'Team association. People can be organized into teams when desired.' => '团队协会。可以根据需要将人员组织成团队。',
'Team members' => '团队成员',
'Team type examples: Prayer team, Hosting team, Usher team, Praise and psalm team' => '团队类型示例：祷告团队，托管团队，亚瑟团队，赞美和诗篇团队',
'Teams' => '小组',
'The CSV import is usually simple enough for many people to succeed. But still you need to do it right. The best way to do a CSV import is to first write one song in by hand into the database. Then export that to a CSV file to see how it looks. Use that as a template for how to import all your songs with CSV.' => 'CSV导入通常很简单，许多人都可以成功。但你仍然需要做得对。执行CSV导入的最佳方法是首先手动将一首歌写入数据库。然后将其导出到CSV文件以查看其外观。使用它作为模板，了解如何使用CSV导入所有歌曲。',
'The ISO Name is very important that you get it exactly right. Several directories are to be named the exact same name.' => 'ISO名称非常重要，您可以完全正确地使用它。几个目录的名称完全相同。',
'The OpenLP import is much easier. The OpenLP format uses one XML file for each song. Zip together all the songs you have exported from OpenLP into one zip file without any subdirectories. Then do the OpenLP import with that ZIP file.' => 'OpenLP导入更容易。 OpenLP格式为每首歌使用一个XML文件。将从OpenLP导出的所有歌曲压缩到一个没有任何子目录的zip文件中。然后使用该ZIP文件执行OpenLP导入。',
'The author of the song. Of course there are authors and music composers and translators. Somehow you need to fit all of these into this field.' => '这首歌的作者。当然还有作家和音乐作曲家和翻译。不知何故，你需要将所有这些都融入这个领域。',
'The church screen is only for the most advanced users. This screen is to manage multiple churches in the same database.  Normally, you will only have one church in one database and then this screen is unnecessary. However, you might see the need for a test church where people can come in and test using \'WorshipHHN\'. Here you could create such a church or any other church if that is needed.' => '教堂屏幕仅适用于最高级用户。此屏幕用于管理同一数据库中的多个教会。通常，您只在一个数据库中拥有一个教堂，然后不需要此屏幕。但是，您可能会看到需要一个测试教会，人们可以使用\'WorshipHHN\'进入并测试。如果需要，你可以在这里创建这样的教堂或任何其他教堂。',
'The definition of the role you can find in the concepts documentation. It is to large to put here.' => '您可以在概念文档中找到角色的定义。放在这里很大。',
'The envelope icon beside each name allows you to send a predefined email to that person. If you don\'t see that envelope icon it is because you don\'t have permissions to do that. There is also a button to send a predefined email to all the persons in this list.' => '每个名称旁边的信封图标允许您向该人发送预定义的电子邮件。如果您没有看到该信封图标，那是因为您没有权限这样做。还有一个按钮可以向此列表中的所有人发送预定义的电子邮件。',
'The event orgainizer will recieve an email notification anytime a task is rejected by a user.' => '只要用户拒绝任务，事件orgainizer就会收到电子邮件通知。',
'The event task list is easy to read and exportable in PDF or EXCEL format.' => '事件任务列表易于阅读并可以PDF或EXCEL格式导出。',
'The following is the list of roles and their meaning. This is a heirarchical list where each time you go up a level you inherit all the permissions of the lower levels. This list is shown from the lowest to the highest level' => '以下是角色列表及其含义。这是一个层次列表，每次上升一级时，您都会继承较低级别的所有权限。此列表显示从最低级别到最高级别',
'The language you wish to view in all the menus and screens' => '您希望在所有菜单和屏幕中查看的语言',
'The messages you define here may or may not require the user to respond by pressing a button that is in the email they receive. There is a lot of flexability in these message definitions.' => '您在此处定义的消息可能需要或可能不需要用户通过按下他们收到的电子邮件中的按钮进行响应。这些消息定义中有很多灵活性。',
'The most important challange here is finding your event. There is a filter to aid in finding the event but this filter is shown as a button. Click on the icon to the right of the filter button and then the filter will open up and you can specify exactly what dates you are interested in seeing. If you hit the button \'clean\' then you will empty the data fields. Then when you hit filter you will get all the defined events. By default you will see only events from today and 3 months forward in time.' => '这里最重要的挑战是找到你的活动。有一个过滤器可帮助查找事件，但此过滤器显示为按钮。单击过滤器按钮右侧的图标，然后过滤器将打开，您可以准确指定您有兴趣看到的日期。如果按“清除”按钮，则会清空数据字段。然后，当您点击过滤器时，您将获得所有已定义的事件。默认情况下，您只会看到今天和3个月前的事件。',
'The most important challange here is finding your task. There is a filter to aid in finding the task but this filter is shown as a button. Click on the icon to the right of the filter button and then the filter will open up and you can specify exactly what dates you are interested in seeing. If you hit the button \'clean\' then you will empty the data fields. Then when you hit filter you will get all the defined tasks. By default you will see only tasks from today and 3 months forward in time.' => '这里最重要的挑战是找到你的任务。有一个过滤器可帮助查找任务，但此过滤器显示为按钮。单击过滤器按钮右侧的图标，然后过滤器将打开，您可以准确指定您有兴趣看到的日期。如果按“清除”按钮，则会清空数据字段。然后，当您点击过滤器时，您将获得所有已定义的任务。默认情况下，您只能看到今天和3个月前的任务。',
'The name of the song. The name that the song is most known by. This data field together with the author is a unique identifier for the record. It is with these two fields an import knows whether to update or add the song.' => '这首歌的名字。这首歌最为人所知的名字。该数据字段与作者一起是记录的唯一标识符。在这两个字段中，导入知道是否更新或添加歌曲。',
'The task lists can also be exported to PDF or EXCEL format.' => '任务列表也可以导出为PDF或EXCEL格式。',
'The task lists can be directly transfered over to your own personal calendar.' => '任务列表可以直接转移到您自己的个人日历。',
'The valid email for the user. It is possible to put here a fake email in the case that your user will probably never log into the system and you don\'t need to have any communications with them.' => '用户的有效电子邮件。如果您的用户可能永远不会登录系统并且您不需要与他们进行任何通信，则可以在此处放置一封虚假的电子邮件。',
'This is a completely translated system at all levels. To achieve this you must define here the languages that you will be using. Probably you have recieved a lot of languages installed when you first installed the system. Feel free to delete any languages you are sure you don\'t want.' => '这是一个完全翻译的系统。要实现此目的，您必须在此定义您将使用的语言。您可能在第一次安装系统时收到了许多安装的语言。随意删除您确定不需要的任何语言。',
'This is a person who has verified his email but not yet been given any permissions at all. This role has no permissions' => '这是一个已经验证了他的电子邮件但尚未获得任何权限的人。此角色没有权限',
'This is an abstraction level in the messaging system that allows you to group together identical message templates that are in different languages. The goal of this grouping is so that a person may get the message in the language that they prefer. Of course, most implementations of this program will only be in one language so that this abstraction level is only an irritation and doesn\'t offer any new functionality.' => '这是消息传递系统中的抽象级别，允许您将不同语言的相同消息模板组合在一起。这种分组的目的是让一个人可以用他们喜欢的语言来获取信息。当然，该程序的大多数实现只能使用一种语言，因此这种抽象级别只是一种烦恼而且不提供任何新功能。',
'This is mainly for the service organizer task.' => '这主要是针对服务组织者的任务。',
'This is only a single name input. Nothing else. The group name.' => '这只是一个单一的名称输入。没有其他的。组名。',
'This is the abstraction that allows the language independence. If you define two or more message templates with the same message type and different languages then you have the ability to send one or the other depending on which language your user prefers.' => '这是允许语言独立的抽象。如果您定义两个或多个具有相同消息类型和不同语言的消息模板，则可以根据用户喜欢的语言发送一个或另一个。',
'This is the body of the email and you must always put something here.  If you want this message to be completely blank to only show the custom message then put something here like a period.' => '这是电子邮件的正文，你必须总是在这里放一些东西。如果您希望此消息完全空白以仅显示自定义消息，则在此处添加类似句点的内容。',
'This is the heart of all configuration for \'WorshipHHN\'. Therefore it is important that you spend time here to make your event management correct. Here is where the contents of all tasks are defined but not the tasks themselves.' => '这是\'WorshipHHN\'所有配置的核心。因此，您必须花时间在这里使事件管理正确。这是定义所有任务的内容而不是任务本身的位置。',
'This is the main screen where everything happens. This one screen is the goal of the entire program. Here you see all the tasks which must be done to ensure a successful event.' => '这是一切都在发生的主屏幕。这一个屏幕是整个计划的目标。在这里，您可以看到为确保事件成功而必须完成的所有任务。',
'This is the song itself. For some installations this could be left blank because only the name is needed in this program. But others may feel the need to put the entire song here because many songs are very similar and also for searching purposes. In the create and update screens this text box has a tab in one corner you can pull on to make the text box as big as you want. Otherwise the text box is very small.' => '这就是歌曲本身。对于某些安装，可以将其留空，因为此程序中只需要名称。但是其他人可能觉得有必要将整首歌放在这里，因为许多歌曲非常相似，也用于搜索目的。在创建和更新屏幕中，此文本框在一个角落中有一个选项卡，您可以将其拉出以使文本框尽可能大。否则文本框非常小。',
'This is very similar to a description however it is more for comunicating specific needs for the task.' => '这与描述非常相似，但更多的是用于传达任务的特定需求。',
'This is where you edit the name of the event and the start and end time of the event. That is all. The main editing is always done by clicking on the task icon' => '您可以在此处编辑事件的名称以及事件的开始和结束时间。就这些。主要编辑始终通过单击任务图标完成',
'This is where you edit the name of the team and the team type.' => '您可以在此处编辑团队名称和团队类型。',
'This is where you edit the profile of the user.' => '您可以在此处编辑用户的个人资料。',
'This must be set to true if the task is not defined for a specific time slot.' => '如果未为特定时间段定义任务，则必须将其设置为true。',
'This name is only for the user to be able to quickly recognize which message this is about?' => '此名称仅供用户快速识别这是什么消息？',
'This screen allows you to find the event plan you need to see or edit. Plus there are many different aspects of the event you can go to from this screen.' => '通过此屏幕，您可以查找需要查看或编辑的活动计划。此外，您可以从此屏幕进入事件的许多不同方面。',
'This screen shows you all the tasks you are scheduled to do in the near future.' => '此屏幕显示您计划在不久的将来执行的所有任务。',
'This screen shows your team all the tasks you are scheduled to do in the near future.' => '此屏幕向您的团队显示您计划在不久的将来执行的所有任务。',
'This will take you to the file sharing area for the specific event. However, inside of the event you can attach files to individual tasks. Here is for putting files that you can\'t find a specific task to attach to.' => '这将带您进入特定事件的文件共享区域。但是，在事件内部，您可以将文件附加到各个任务。这是用于放置您无法找到要附加的特定任务的文件。',
'This will take you to the file sharing area for the team.' => '这将带您进入团队的文件共享区域。',
'Unavailability' => '不可用',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to five icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the event or perform an action on the event plan. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜单”列下，您可以看到最多五个图标，具体取决于您的权限级别。每个图标都会将您发送到活动的不同方面或对活动计划执行操作。图标定义如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to six icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the event or perform an action on the event plan. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜单”列下，您可以看到最多六个图标，具体取决于您的权限级别。每个图标都会将您发送到活动的不同方面或对活动计划执行操作。图标定义如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to six icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the team or perform an action on the team. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜单”列下，您可以看到最多六个图标，具体取决于您的权限级别。每个图标都会将您发送到团队的不同方面或对团队执行操作。图标定义如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up two icons depending on what your permission level is. They are for accepting or rejecting the task. In some installations this might be your primary way of accepting or rejecting tasks. Or it might be done in emails instead. Consult your system administrator to find out how it will be done.' => '在“菜单”列下，您可以看到两个图标，具体取决于您的权限级别。它们用于接受或拒绝任务。在某些安装中，这可能是您接受或拒绝任务的主要方式。或者它可能在电子邮件中完成。请咨询您的系统管理员，了解如何完成。',
