'We think this program is a simple and powerful tool you can use to plan events for your church. We use it to plan all our church services.' => '我们认为这个程序是一个简单而强大的工具，可用于为教会规划活动。我们用它来计划我们所有的教会服务。',
'What language will this message be in? This is an important part of being able to send the same message to different persons in different languages' => '这条消息将以什么语言出现？这是能够以不同语言向不同人发送相同消息的重要部分',
'When you have more then one church, you must remember that each church is completely seperate from another church. There is nothing common between the churches. Therefore for each new church you must create everything from the beginning.' => '如果你有一个以上的教会，你必须记住，每个教会都完全独立于另一个教会。教会之间没有什么共同之处。因此，对于每个新教会，你必须从一开始就创造出一切。',
'Will a bible verse need to be defined so others can coordinate the showing of that verse? Or possibly just tell others what bible verses you plan to use.' => '是否需要定义圣经经文以便其他人可以协调该节经文的展示？或者可能只是告诉别人你打算用什么圣经经文。',
'Will a team be needed or used to do this task?' => '是否需要团队来完成这项任务？',
